Multiphysics Application Coupling Toolkit
-----------------------------------------
QuickStart for the impatient:
MPI and HDF4 are required.
CC=mpicc (or equivalent)
CXX=mpicxx (or equivalent)
FC=mpif90 (or equivalent)
CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/arbitrary/install/path (optional)

> cmake /path/to/mpact/source
> make
> make install (optional)
-----------------------------------------